{center}
{subhead}Amiga Forever 5.0  (16/11/01){def}
{left}
{pp}
Amiga Forever 5.0 is now available in a CD-ROM, CD-ROM Upgrade,
Online Edition, Online Upgrade and Cross-Platform Online Edition.
{pp}
Amiga Forever contains latest software to satisfy two major needs of
 many Amiga users: to use their existing Amiga software and data on non-Amiga
hardware, and to share data between Amiga and other systems.
{pp}
It includes latest version of the Emulators (JIT), Kickstart ROMs (including the
CDTV and CD32 versions), Picasso96, PPaint 7.1b, Disk2FDI and Workbenchs
upto 3.1, Software Manager,  and MPEG videos of Jay Miner and the Deathbed video.
{pp}
Additionally, software, tutorial and reference files which are likely to be
of interest to any Amiga enthusiast are included.
{pp}
Tested with Windows XP as well.
{pp}
